leetcode 1614 

appraoch with soln explain : 

class Solution {
    public int maxDepth(String s) {
       
        int maxi = 0 ;      // maximum depth track karne ke liye
        int open = 0 ;      // abhi tak kitne '(' open hain

        for(int i= 0 ; i< s.length() ; i++){
            if(s.charAt(i) == '('){
                open++;  
                // jab naya '(' mila, depth ek level badh gayi
                maxi = Math.max(maxi , open); 
                // max depth update karna
            }
            else if(s.charAt(i) == ')'){
                open--;  
                // ek bracket close hua, depth ek level kam ho gayi
            }
        }
        return maxi;   // finally max depth return
    }
}


This question or any question with nesting max parenthesis is solve using STACK  , whenever you see parenthesis always think about stack first . its like SANKET . 
